rows.label: tlk43300061_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Heyah. You're tourists, too? Me and
my family are also traveling. We spent
a few days chilling in Iyasaki.

rows.label: tlk43300061_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But now, ah... The time we've spent
waiting for a boat is longer than our
original holiday. Crazy, right?

rows.label: tlk43300061_01_msg0003
rows.name:
They told us that a boat bound
for Superbia should soon be leaving
from Rigitte Harbor, but...

rows.label: tlk43300061_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't really see me taking
my whole family across that
ridge in the Cloud Sea...

rows.label: tlk43300061_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Not to mention, us Invidians
going to Superbia might get a
bit hairy in its own right...
